                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-635" type="surname" value="HILDITCH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-635" type="given" value="WILLIAM UNWIN"></interp>WILLIAM UNWIN HILDITCH</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Susannah-row, Dorset-street.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184004060091"></xptr>
               <p>On Saturday night, the 14th of March, I was going past the prosecutor's shop, and saw the prisoner stoop and pick up a pair of trowsers at Mr. Newman's step—he rolled them up in hit arms, and ran away—I told Jones of it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I taw them lying down, I picked them up, not off the step, but off the ground—I did not know whose they were.</p>
